<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="eyebrow">紫微斗数 · 四柱八字</view>
    <view class="title" bindlongpress="openSettings">谈玄机</view>
    <view class="summary">输入出生日期、时辰和性别，生成命盘摘要，并把传统术语翻译成更容易理解的分项解读。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="actions">
    <button class="primary" bindtap="openNativeApp">开始排盘</button>
    <view class="secondary-actions">
      <button class="secondary" bindtap="openCompliance">使用说明</button>
      <button class="secondary" open-type="share">分享给朋友</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{hasAdUnit}}" class="ad-wrap {{adHidden ? 'ad-wrap-hidden' : ''}}">
    <ad-custom
      wx:if="{{adCustomUnitId}}"
      unit-id="{{adCustomUnitId}}"
      bindload="handleAdLoad"
      binderror="handleAdError"
    />
    <ad
      wx:else
      unit-id="{{adBannerUnitId}}"
      ad-intervals="60"
      bindload="handleAdLoad"
      binderror="handleAdError"
    />
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="row" bindtap="openCompliance">
      <view>
        <view class="row-title">传统文化参考</view>
        <view class="row-text">解读不构成确定性判断，重要事项请结合现实信息做决定</view>
      </view>
      <view class="chevron">›</view>
    </view>
    <view class="row" bindtap="openNativeApp">
      <view>
        <view class="row-title">小程序内生成</view>
        <view class="row-text">出生信息只保存在本机微信，解读按本次问询日期关联保存</view>
      </view>
      <view class="chevron">›</view>
    </view>
    <view class="row" bindtap="copyUrl">
      <view>
        <view class="row-title">复制网页版地址</view>
        <view class="row-text">{{siteUrl}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="chevron">›</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice">
    生成解读会发送当前命盘摘要到后端模型服务；报告会保存在当前微信本机缓存中，可随时清除。
  </view>
</view>
